Description: CVE-2026-32636 - Fix out of bounds write in ConvertUTF16ToUTF8
 Corrected out of bounds write of a single zero byte in ConvertUTF16ToUTF8
 in magick/xml-tree.c. The ResizeQuantumMemory call did not account for
 the null terminator byte, leading to a heap buffer overflow when writing
 the trailing '\0'.
Origin: upstream, https://github.com/ImageMagick/ImageMagick6/commit/a04a9a514c70c9533ccb9f6ff80102a1b9a6445b
Author: Cristy <urban-warrior@imagemagick.org>
Last-Update: 2026-03-19

--- a/magick/xml-tree.c
+++ b/magick/xml-tree.c
@@ -1359,7 +1359,7 @@
     }
   }
   *length=(size_t) j;
-  utf8=(char *) ResizeQuantumMemory(utf8,*length,sizeof(*utf8));
+  utf8=(char *) ResizeQuantumMemory(utf8,(*length+1),sizeof(*utf8));
   if (utf8 != (char *) NULL)
     utf8[*length]='\0';
   return(utf8);
Description: CVE-2026-25966 - Block fd: filenames in security policies
 ImageMagick's security policy blocks stdin/stdout access (pattern="-")
 but does not block file descriptor access (fd:0, fd:1, etc.), allowing
 policy bypass. This patch adds a blocking rule for fd:* patterns.
Origin: upstream, commit:2c2f87de5330cd895fab9ea6228577b30acd1c7a
Author: Cristy <urban-warrior@imagemagick.org>
Last-Update: 2026-01-28

--- a/config/policy.xml
+++ b/config/policy.xml
@@ -80,2 +80,4 @@
   <!-- <policy domain="system" name="font" value="/path/to/font.ttf"/> -->
+  <!-- Don't read/write from/to stdin/stdout or file descriptors. -->
+  <policy domain="path" rights="none" pattern="fd:*" />
 </policymap>
Description: CVE-2026-26983 - Fix use-after-free in MSL interpreter map element handling
 ImageMagick's MSL interpreter encounters a use-after-free condition when
 handling an invalid <map> element. When the affinity_image is NULL (due to
 no valid image attribute), RemapImages() is called with a NULL pointer and
 DestroyImage() is called on it, causing a crash. This patch adds a null
 check around RemapImages() and DestroyImage() calls, and reorders
 DestroyQuantizeInfo() to occur after the conditional block.
Origin: upstream, https://github.com/ImageMagick/ImageMagick6/commit/b34591e9067df9cd6fe73b71b1f0d20b3c2bbbc0
Author: Cristy <urban-warrior@imagemagick.org>
Last-Update: 2025-02-25

